
# Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 12 December 2025

This Privacy Policy describes how **AM DEVS SOFT** ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and protects the personal information of users of the application **"Dawam – Employee Companion"** ("Dawam", "the App", or "the Service").

By installing or using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

### Personal Information

To provide and improve our services, we may collect certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to:

* Name
* Email address
* Gender
* Location
* Profile picture
* Any information you voluntarily provide within the App

This information is used solely for providing, improving, and maintaining App functionality.

### Device Information

We may collect non-identifiable information from your device, such as:

* Device model
* Operating system version
* App usage data
* Error logs

This information helps us improve performance, ensure security, and prevent fraudulent activity.

### Location Information

Some features may use location data obtained from your mobile device.
We only use this information for features that require location and solely for the purpose intended by the App.

### Cookies

The App itself does not use cookies.
However, third-party services integrated into the App may use cookies to improve their functionality.

---

## 2. Third-Party Services

The App may use third-party services that could collect data used to identify you.
We may employ external companies and individuals for:

* Facilitating the Service
* Providing service-related functions
* Performing service support
* Analyzing how the App is used

These third parties may access your data only to perform tasks on our behalf and are prohibited from sharing or using it for any other purpose.

---

## 3. Data Security

We are committed to protecting your personal information.
However, no electronic transmission or storage method is completely secure.
While we strive to use commercially acceptable methods to protect your data, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

---

## 4. Children’s Privacy

The App is not intended for children under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
If such information is found to have been collected, it will be deleted immediately.

---

## 5. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be posted on this page and become effective immediately upon posting.
You are advised to review this page periodically for updates.

---

